## 4. Deep Linking (OAuth, Magic Links)

### 4.1 URL Scheme Configuration

**In `app.config.ts`:**
```typescript
export default {
  scheme: 'hestia',
  ios: {
    bundleIdentifier: 'app.justhestia.ios',
    associatedDomains: ['applinks:hestia.com'],
  },
  android: {
    package: 'app.justhestia.ios',
    intentFilters: [
      {
        action: 'VIEW',
        data: [
          {
            scheme: 'https',
            host: 'hestia.com',
            pathPrefix: '/auth',
          },
        ],
        category: ['BROWSABLE', 'DEFAULT'],
      },
    ],
  },
}
```

**Supported URLs:**
- `hestia://auth/callback` (custom scheme)
- `https://hestia.com/auth/callback` (universal links)

